unk-viral-love-child-post-circulating-on-social-media-3793929">揭穿了社交媒体上疯传的“私生子”帖子</a>，其中一名 Instagram 用户声称自己是孩子的母亲。</p><p> Hellfest 2025 将于 6 月 19 日至 22 日在法国克利松举行。其他已确认演出的乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/frank-carter">Frank Carter 的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sex-pistols">Sex Pistols</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spiritbox">Spiritbox</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/exodus">Exodus</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/judas-priest">Judas Priest</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/turnstile">Turnstile</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dream-theater">Dream Theater</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/refused">Refused</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cypress-hill">Cypress Hill</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/falling-in-reverse">Falling in Reverse</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/knocked-loose">Knocked Loose</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eagles-of-death-metal">Eagles Of Death Metal</a> 。</p><p> Hellfest 创始人首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上，声称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-cancelled-planned-2025-tour-claims-hellfest-founder-3821087">喷火战机“取消”了计划于 2025 年进行的巡演</a>。</p> ;
